                                                    </span>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mt-2" style=" color: #212529">
                                        <li>
                                            <h5>1. Sinto-me tenso ou contraído</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q1_1" name="q1" value="1" @(Model.q1 != null && Model.q1 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q1_1">A maior parte das vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q1_2" name="q1" value="2" @(Model.q1 != null && Model.q1 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q1_2">Muitas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q1_3" name="q1" value="3" @(Model.q1 != null && Model.q1 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q1_3">De vez em quando, ocasionalmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q1_4" name="q1" value="4" @(Model.q1 != null && Model.q1 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q1_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>2. Continuo a ter prazer nas mesmas coisas de antes</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q2_1" name="q2" value="1" @(Model.q2 != null && Model.q2 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q2_1">Tanto como antes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q2_2" name="q2" value="2" @(Model.q2 != null && Model.q2 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q2_2">Não tanto como antes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q2_3" name="q2" value="3" @(Model.q2 != null && Model.q2 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q2_3">Só um pouco</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q2_4" name="q2" value="4" @(Model.q2 != null && Model.q2 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q2_4">Quase nada</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>3. Tenho uma sensação de medo como se algo estivesse para acontecer</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q3_1" name="q3" value="1" @(Model.q3 != null && Model.q3 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q3_1">Tanto como antes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q3_2" name="q3" value="2" @(Model.q3 != null && Model.q3 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q3_2">Não tanto como antes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q3_3" name="q3" value="3" @(Model.q3 != null && Model.q3 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q3_3">Só um pouco</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q3_4" name="q3" value="4" @(Model.q3 != null && Model.q3 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q3_4">Quase nada</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>4. Sou capaz de rir e de ver o lado divertido das situações</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q4_1" name="q4" value="1" @(Model.q4 != null && Model.q4 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q4_1">Tanto como habitualmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q4_2" name="q4" value="2" @(Model.q4 != null && Model.q4 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q4_2">Não tanto como hatiualmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q4_3" name="q4" value="3" @(Model.q4 != null && Model.q4 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q4_3">Nitidamente menos</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q4_4" name="q4" value="4" @(Model.q4 != null && Model.q4 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q4_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>5. Tenho a cabeça cheia de preocupações</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q5_1" name="q5" value="1" @(Model.q5 != null && Model.q5 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q5_1">A maior parte do tempo</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q5_2" name="q5" value="2" @(Model.q5 != null && Model.q5 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q5_2">Muitas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q5_3" name="q5" value="3" @(Model.q5 != null && Model.q5 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q5_3">De vez em quando</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q5_4" name="q5" value="4" @(Model.q5 != null && Model.q5 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q5_4">Raramente</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>6. Sinto-me bem disposto</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q6_1" name="q6" value="1" @(Model.q6 != null && Model.q6 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q6_1">Nunca</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q6_2" name="q6" value="2" @(Model.q6 != null && Model.q6 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q6_2">Poucas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q6_3" name="q6" value="3" @(Model.q6 != null && Model.q6 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q6_3">Bastantes vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q6_4" name="q6" value="4" @(Model.q6 != null && Model.q6 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q6_4">Quase sempre</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>7. Sou capaz de estar à vontade e sentir-me relaxado</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q7_1" name="q7" value="1" @(Model.q7 != null && Model.q7 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q7_1">Sempre</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q7_2" name="q7" value="2" @(Model.q7 != null && Model.q7 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q7_2">Habitualmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q7_3" name="q7" value="3" @(Model.q7 != null && Model.q7 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q7_3">Algumas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q7_4" name="q7" value="4" @(Model.q7 != null && Model.q7 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q7_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>8. Sinto-me lento</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q8_1" name="q8" value="1" @(Model.q8 != null && Model.q8 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q8_1">Quase sempre</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q8_2" name="q8" value="2" @(Model.q8 != null && Model.q8 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q8_2">Com muita frequência</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q8_3" name="q8" value="3" @(Model.q8 != null && Model.q8 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q8_3">Algumas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q8_4" name="q8" value="4" @(Model.q8 != null && Model.q8 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q8_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>9. Por vezes fico tão assustado que até sinto um aperto no estômago</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q9_1" name="q9" value="1" @(Model.q9 != null && Model.q9 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q9_1">Nunca</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q9_2" name="q9" value="2" @(Model.q9 != null && Model.q9 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q9_2">De vez em quando</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q9_3" name="q9" value="3" @(Model.q9 != null && Model.q9 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q9_3">Muitas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q9_4" name="q9" value="4" @(Model.q9 != null && Model.q9 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q9_4">Quase sempre</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>10. Perdi o meu interesse em cuidar no meu aspecto</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q10_1" name="q10" value="1" @(Model.q10 != null && Model.q10 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q10_1">Completamente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q10_2" name="q10" value="2" @(Model.q10 != null && Model.q10 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q10_2">Não tenho tanto cuidado como devia</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q10_3" name="q10" value="3" @(Model.q10 != null && Model.q10 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q10_3">Talvez menos interesse do que antes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q10_4" name="q10" value="4" @(Model.q10 != null && Model.q10 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q10_4">O mesmo interesse de sempre</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>11. Sinto-me impaciente e não consigo estar parado</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q11_1" name="q11" value="1" @(Model.q11 != null && Model.q11 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q11_1">Sempre</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q11_2" name="q11" value="2" @(Model.q11 != null && Model.q11 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q11_2">Habitualmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q11_3" name="q11" value="3" @(Model.q11 != null && Model.q11 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q11_3">Algumas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q11_4" name="q11" value="4" @(Model.q11 != null && Model.q11 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q11_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>12. Penso com prazer nas coisas futuras</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q12_1" name="q12" value="1" @(Model.q12 != null && Model.q12 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q12_1">Tanto como habitualmente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q12_2" name="q12" value="2" @(Model.q12 != null && Model.q12 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q12_2">Menos que anteriormente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q12_3" name="q12" value="3" @(Model.q12 != null && Model.q12 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q12_3">Bastante menos que anteriormente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q12_4" name="q12" value="4" @(Model.q12 != null && Model.q12 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q12_4">Quase nada</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>13. Tenho sensações súbitas de pânico</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q13_1" name="q13" value="1" @(Model.q13 != null && Model.q13 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q13_1">Com grande frequência</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q13_2" name="q13" value="2" @(Model.q13 != null && Model.q13 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q13_2">Bastantes vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q13_3" name="q13" value="3" @(Model.q13 != null && Model.q13 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q13_3">Algumas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q13_4" name="q13" value="4" @(Model.q13 != null && Model.q13 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q13_4">Nunca</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="mt-2">
                                            <h5>14. Sinto-me capaz de apreciar um bom livro ou um bom programa de rádio ou TV</h5>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q14_1" name="q14" value="1" @(Model.q14 != null && Model.q14 == 1 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q14_1">Frequentemente</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q14_2" name="q14" value="2" @(Model.q14 != null && Model.q14 == 2 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q14_2">Algumas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q14_3" name="q14" value="3" @(Model.q14 != null && Model.q14 == 3 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q14_3">Poucas vezes</label></li>
                                                <li><input type="radio" id="q14_4" name="q14" value="4" @(Model.q14 != null && Model.q14 == 4 ? "checked" : "") /> <label for="q14_4">Muito raramente</label></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <!--  DATATABLE START -->
                            <div class="card mb-32pt">
                                <div class="card-header">
                                    <div class="form-inline">
                                        <label class="" for="length_change">Mostrar</label>
                                        <select class="custom-select length_change mb-2 mr-sm-2 mb-sm-0" data-id="GTQuestTable">
                                            <option value='10'>10</option>
                                            <option value='25'>25</option>
                                            <option value='50'>50</option>
                                            <option value='100'>100</option>
                                            <option value='500'>500</option>
                                            <option value='1000'>1000</option>
                                            <option value='2000'>2000</option>
                                            <option value='5000'>5000</option>
                                            <option value='10000'>10000</option>
                                        </select>
                                        <label class="" for="length_change">registos</label>
                                        <div class="btn-group">
                                            <button type="button" title="Selecionar" id="btnSelect" class="btnSelect btn btn-default" data-id="GTQuestTable"><i class="fa fa-check-square"></i></button>
                                            @if (AcessControl.Authorized(AcessControl.GT_QUEST_ANXIETY_DELETE))
                                            {<button type="button" title="Remover selecionado(s)" class="open-modal-crud RemoverMultiplos btn btn-default" data-id="0" data-action="RemoverMultiplos" data-upload="GT_RespAnsiedadeDepressao" data-entity="gtquest" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#crudControlModal" disabled=""><i class="fa fa-trash"></i></button>
                                            } <button type="button" title="Pesquisar" class="btnSearch btn btn-default" data-id="GTQuestTable"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
                                            <button type="button" title="Limpar Filtro" class="btnLimpar btn btn-default" data-id="GTQuestTable"><i class="fa fa-eraser"></i></button>
                                            <!--Separator-->
                                            <a title="Exportar filtro (.xlsx)" class="btnSearch btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("ExportToExcel", "XLSReports", new { section = "gtquest", applyFilter = "true" })" target="_blank" data-id="GTQuestTable"><i class="fa fa-filter"></i></a>
                                            <a title="Exportar todos (.xlsx)" class="btnSearch btn btn-default" href="@Url.Action("ExportToExcel", "XLSReports", new { section = "gtquest", applyFilter = "false" })" target="_blank" data-id="GTQuestTable"><i class="fa fa-file-excel"></i></a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="table-responsive">
                                    <table id="GTQuestTable" class="hideInputCheck table table-hover mb-0 thead-border-top-0 table-nowrap">
                                        <thead>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td></td>
                                                <td></td>
                                                <td><input type="text" id="GTQuestTableTreino" class="form-control form-control-sm" /></td>
                                                <td><input type="text" id="GTQuestTableInsercao" class="form-control form-control-sm" /></td>
                                                <td><input type="text" id="GTQuestTableDataInsercao" class="form-control form-control-sm datepicker" /></td>
                                                <td><input type="text" id="GTQuestTableActualizacao" class="form-control form-control-sm" /></td>
                                                <td><input type="text" id="GTQuestTableDataActualizacao" class="form-control form-control-sm datepicker" /></td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th></th>
                                                <th></th>
                                                <th data-name="GTQuestTableTreino">&nbsp;</th>
                                                <th data-name="GTQuestTableInsercao">Inserção</th>
                                                <th data-name="GTQuestTableDataInsercao">Data Inserção</th>
                                                <th data-name="GTQuestTableActualizacao">Actualização</th>
                                                <th data-name="GTQuestTableDataActualizacao">Data Actualização</th>
                                            </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                    </table>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-footer p-8pt">
                                    <span class="paginateInfoGTQuestTable paginateInfo mr-12pt" style="float:right"></span>
                                    <div id="paginateGTQuestTable" class="pagination justify-content-start pagination-xsm m-0"></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!--  DATATABLE START -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
        <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
    </div>
    <!-- /page content -->
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function (event) {
            handleDataGTQuestTable();
        });
    </script>
}
else
{
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function (event) {
            $('#selecionaravaliado').click();
        });
    </script>
}